---

## 💡 Key Contributions

* Integration of **synthetic negative controls** for improved training
* Introduction of **target accessibility feature**
* Implementation of **feature-consistent dataset pipeline**
* Fully reproducible **Docker-based ML workflow**

---

## ⚠️ Limitations

* Small dataset size
* Synthetic negatives may not fully represent biological non-interactions
* Approximate accessibility (not RNAplfold-based)

---

## 🚀 Future Work

* Integrate **RNAplfold-based accessibility**
* Expand dataset with high-throughput interaction data
* Use advanced models (XGBoost, Deep Learning)
* Improve feature engineering (binding site localization)

